## Technology-Specific Notes

### React Three Fiber (R3F)

#### Key Learning
R3F v9 has significant API changes from v8. Always check the latest documentation.

#### Common Pitfalls
- Never use `useFrame` outside of Canvas context
- `Html` component from drei requires `transform` prop for 3D positioning
- InstancedMesh color changes require `needsUpdate = true` on the attribute

#### Correct Usage
```typescript
// Correct way to update InstancedMesh colors
mesh.instanceColor!.needsUpdate = true;

// Correct Html positioning in 3D
<Html position={[x, y, z]} transform occlude={false}>
  <div>Content</div>
</Html>
```

